â–ªï¸If an input array is sorted then
- Binary search
- Two pointers

â–ªï¸If asked for all permutations/subsets then
- Backtracking

â–ªï¸If given a tree then
- DFS
- BFS

â–ªï¸If given a graph then
- DFS
- BFS

â–ªï¸If given a linked list then
- Two pointers

â–ªï¸If recursion is banned then
- Stack

â–ªï¸If must solve in-place then
- Swap corresponding values
- Store one or more different values in the same pointer

â–ªï¸If asked for maximum/minumum subarray/subset/options then
- Dynamic programming

â–ªï¸If asked for top/least K items then
- Heap

â–ªï¸If asked for common strings then
- Map
- Trie

â–ªï¸If asked for find minimum k integer within  k times
- Binary Search

â–ªï¸Else
- Map/Set for O(1) time & O(n) space
- Sort input for O(nlogn) time and O(1) space


